Grand design:

	- Something that boots on 8086, 80286, 80386 and AMD Opteron and uses its modern features.
	- Implement several games (sokoban, snake, pong) + PC speaker + Sound Blaster.
	- Implement filesystem, maybe FAT12.
	- It should fit to 3.5'' 1.44M floppy diskette.

